Can I help you?

19:07.494 --> 19:09.583
Excuse me, sweetie?

19:09.626 --> 19:12.629
You've been following me
since I got on the 5.

19:12.673 --> 19:14.762
Oh. I'm sorry.

19:14.805 --> 19:17.852
I...I was headed up to Camp Redwood.

19:17.895 --> 19:20.202
These were the directions
I was given.

19:20.246 --> 19:22.465
Oh.
God.

19:22.509 --> 19:25.033
Oh, I am so sorry.

19:25.076 --> 19:27.427
It's just... you hear all thesehorror stories on the news

19:27.470 --> 19:29.211
and they always start
with a single woman

19:29.255 --> 19:31.996
driving alone and that woman
ends up in a garbage bag

19:32.040 --> 19:33.433
by the side of the road.

19:33.476 --> 19:36.479
Goodness, you have
a dark imagination.

19:38.525 --> 19:40.483
I'm headed to Camp Redwood, too.

19:40.527 --> 19:42.311
I'm actually gonna
be the nurse there.

19:42.355 --> 19:44.313
Hey, would you do me a favor?

19:44.357 --> 19:46.489
Can you keep an eye on my car
while I head to the ladies'?

19:46.533 --> 19:48.012
Maybe we can convoy up

19:48.056 --> 19:50.232
-the rest of the way there.
-Works for me.

19:50.276 --> 19:52.452
We girls got to look out
for each other.

19:52.495 --> 19:54.323
Great.

19:58.719 --> 20:00.677
If you ask me,
all those murders

20:00.721 --> 20:03.941
are because of the availabilityof pornography

20:03.985 --> 20:06.205
and the objectification
of women in our culture.

20:07.423 --> 20:09.686
That's what that Ted Bundy said.

