♪ Oh, oh, here she comes♪

21:39.428 --> 21:41.517
♪ Watch out, boy,
she'll chew you up.♪

21:50.396 --> 21:52.049
My legs...
What did you give me?

21:52.093 --> 21:55.226
Horse tranquilizers.
I think.

21:55.270 --> 21:56.967
I mean, I'm not a nurse.

21:57.011 --> 21:59.535
My degree's in psychology.

22:23.472 --> 22:25.561
Chet, are you with me?
Chet.

22:28.651 --> 22:29.957
Chet.

22:30.000 --> 22:31.524
Look, you just passed out
from the pain, man.

22:31.567 --> 22:33.613
You'll be okay.

22:33.656 --> 22:35.876
Goddamn it.

22:35.919 --> 22:38.095
I didn't even want to come here!

22:39.532 --> 22:41.838
I only left L.A.
'cause I'm in trouble.

